strategy-runner
==============

This programe is an implementation of Technical Assignment of Inegnsoma Arbitrage Pte.

Installation
------------

strategy-runner was developed and tested on Ubuntu 18.04.
The plotting library requires python and matplotlib, that means you have to have a pyhon Installation first.
On ubuntu, simplely run following commands:
    sudo apt update
    sudo apt install python-matplotlib python-numpy python2.7-dev.

Next to compiler it:
    ./configure --prefix=<installed dir>
    make && make install

Create a directory called `data` in <installed dir>, then put market datafiles into this directory.
start startegy-runner by:
    ./runner